Attention,
If you're a child that feels lost or completely hopeless and in need of guidance and assistance, this email is
for you. When you build a door, opportunity awaits you. This is one of those opportunities and this may
change your life!
We are Techie Youth, a non-profit organization that helps foster children and in danger & at-risk youth
children to develop them professionals to thrive in modern day world. Techie Youth focuses mainly on
at-risk youth populations who are facing extreme life-challenges and those who are in guidance
and assistance to learn how to become financially independent. Many students in our
organization were statistically likely to become homeless or incarcerated. Knowing those odds,
we have helped thousands of students alter their life to become independent adults with our
services. With over 3,000+ students with locations throughout NYC including Long Island City,
Bushwick, Brooklyn and locations in Long Island, techie youth provide an urban workplace for
the youth and many of the students are seen on TV such as Fox 5, Pix 11 and abc channel for
their outstanding work. To learn more, watch this video:
(19) What is Techie Youth? How we help foster teens & at-risk youth... - YouTube
Our organization offers a variety of skills to teach. We understand many of you are not sure what
you want to do with your life. In fact, you are all teenagers, so it's not expected for you to have
everything figured out. And a lot of teenagers are very lost in life with no moral nor financial
support from anyone. We believe that teenagers are the future of the world that will advance the
world to a new age. Most teenagers need the right guidance and support and that is what we are
here for.
Do you want to start your own business? We can teach you everything there is to know about
making money and even strategies you can do RIGHT NOW to make fast cash. You are
interested in creating art, we can help you learn digital skills that can bring your artistic gifts into
the world and get PAID for it. You love making music, we can help you become a musician and
compose your own music. There are way more classes we offer such as artificial intelligence,
video editing, creating digital art using photoshop and selling them, trading stocks and
cryptocurrencies, writing content, earning income using social media, create your own website,
creating a video game, music production, creating mobile apps, and so much more. There is
something for everyone to learn and enjoy. These are just an example of loads of classes we
offer.
Now imagine this, you find a skill you genuinely love doing and get paid to live the lifestyle you
deserve. There is a saying that when you love what you do, you never have to work a day in your
life.
We are aware that many of you are in extremely difficult circumstances, so Techie Youth
designed this program to best suit your current conditions. All that is required is your ability to
speak English and a device with internet connection. And the best part is,
It's completely FREE!!!!!!!!!
All we ask for is your time and your effort!
No matter who you are, even if you know NOTHING, we will mold you into a self-sufficient
adult. Let us mentor you.
